In Design Critiques, UX Engineers meet with the Design Manager at least once per sprint to present their design progress and planning for group discussion.

<span key="c03e652527c04a18b0e803c0fd5d95b3"><span offset-key="c03e652527c04a18b0e803c0fd5d95b3:0"><span slate-zero-width="n">â€‹</span></span></span>

## 

<span key="1a0cb929d9964a14af54272a089c8798"><span offset-key="1a0cb929d9964a14af54272a089c8798:0">What are Design Critiques?</span></span>

<span key="f956f283d3414bb5a67e68794abc48d1"><span offset-key="f956f283d3414bb5a67e68794abc48d1:0">In Design Critiques, UX Engineers meet with the Design Manager at least once per sprint to present their design progress and planning for group discussion.</span></span>

## 

<span key="13ead3a88bc44e3b881d0704f979d0d3"><span offset-key="13ead3a88bc44e3b881d0704f979d0d3:0">Our Goals</span></span>

<span key="7d99c7ea28264248b360e9e412a28ec7">**Go Deeper on Core Design Concepts**</span>

<span key="4b977fa5351e4a308110543f0a58b94e"><span offset-key="4b977fa5351e4a308110543f0a58b94e:0">These sessions are an opportunity to empower you with a more nuanced understanding of UI/UX that you can </span>**carry into interviews**<span offset-key="4b977fa5351e4a308110543f0a58b94e:2">.</span></span>

<span key="4a046769bf224902ae06cb9d2d1c5497">**Reinforce the Curriculum**</span>

<span key="ea3eab657e23403184c233288c56f46c"><span offset-key="ea3eab657e23403184c233288c56f46c:0">By walking through active projects together throughout development, we'll naturally encounter </span>**clear, real-world case studies**<span offset-key="ea3eab657e23403184c233288c56f46c:2"> that provide examples of best practices.</span></span>

<span key="d889ffb298024ddf97a1d36617898126">**Level Up Your Product's Quality**</span>

<span key="cf714925848a48758aefcbdf5bc78450"><span offset-key="cf714925848a48758aefcbdf5bc78450:0">Design Critiques are a great opportunity to practice </span>**giving and receiving feedback**<span offset-key="cf714925848a48758aefcbdf5bc78450:2"> in the context of team development.</span></span>

## 

<span key="f23c033e8f55484db724ae63e8e10ea0"><span offset-key="f23c033e8f55484db724ae63e8e10ea0:0">Agenda</span></span>

### 

<span key="eab05f75611d496686d333f938507157"><span offset-key="eab05f75611d496686d333f938507157:0">Pick Volunteers</span></span>

<span key="b87be493cd614d4680a9b67dc898e3b9"><span offset-key="b87be493cd614d4680a9b67dc898e3b9:0">We'll pick on a few UX Engineers to walk us through what they're working on!</span></span>

### 

<span key="307a739ee2d1427e93d1f8b85e3d2f3d"><span offset-key="307a739ee2d1427e93d1f8b85e3d2f3d:0">Design Lead Presentations</span></span>

<span key="b0946cfcbd214f358dc738bf36f48691">**Introduction**</span>

<span key="51b3989a06654435ad2c441d75ea859b"><span offset-key="51b3989a06654435ad2c441d75ea859b:0">Each UX Engineer on the presenting team should give a </span>*very brief*<span offset-key="51b3989a06654435ad2c441d75ea859b:2"> introduction of themselves and their design experience, then they should introduce their product to provide context.</span></span>

<span key="b2137b62dc1f4102823a4b54741c0460">**Product Demo**</span>

<span key="6b5d692715e942a9adf7823913738cd9"><span offset-key="6b5d692715e942a9adf7823913738cd9:0">With someone sharing their screen, the UX Engineer should collaboratively walk through either the live deployed version or a relevant local version of the product. The Design Manager facilitates a group discussion identifying aspects of the product demonstrating good UI/UX principles as well as aspects needing improvement.</span></span>

<span key="d8654126133d415eaedc2e32251e8b20">**Planning Artifact Presentation**</span>

<span key="5612caa89da94a82830d619171e1711c"><span offset-key="5612caa89da94a82830d619171e1711c:0">With someone sharing their screen, the Design Leads should collaboratively walk through any design planning artifacts they've got (e.g. user flows, wireframes). The Design Manager facilitates a group discussion about the artifacts, the general design direction, and UI/UX concerns relevant to their product.</span></span>

<span key="fc61cc268a4942fb9cb7b22bee2dd991"><span offset-key="fc61cc268a4942fb9cb7b22bee2dd991:0">Now read on to see how </span>**Product Reviews**<span offset-key="fc61cc268a4942fb9cb7b22bee2dd991:2"> work in Labs.</span></span>
